700027f-a.title: Bronx: 132nd Street (East) - Cypress Avenue
700027f-a.text:
East 132nd Street, north side, west from (No. 703) a point east
of Cypress Ave.
April 12, 1931.
P. L. Sperr.

700841f-b.title: Bronx: Cypress Avenue - 132nd Street (North)
700841f-b.text:
(1)
Cypress Ave. (extreme left), north from East 132nd Street (fore-
ground), showing the clearance, on the east side of the avenue, created
for the construction of an approach to the Triborough Bridge. lIt extends
to East 135th Street. In the left foreground is the Jacob Doll piano
factory.
September 26, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
Part of the same (extreme right center in View 1), as viewed eastward.
September 26, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
(3)
The same as view 1, at a later date.
